<C>__{sarah}
<D>__{we got it!}
<A>__{he grins and she kisses him on the cheek. elle, shoved to the back, tries to get closer, when she hears —}
<C>__{enid}
<D>__{the competition must not have been that stiff.}
<A>__{arrogant aaron pushes his way to the board.}
<C>__{arrogant aaron}
<D>__{why? ion .got a spot?}
