<A>__{elle, now next to him, gets a look at the board.}
<C>__{elle}
<P>__{(shocked)}
<D>__{me?!}
<A>__{everyone reacts. she turns and faces the throng. they stare back at her in shock. dignified, she walks through them as they part for her, stopping in front of warner and sarah.}
<C>__{elle }
<P>__{(continuing; to warner)}
<D>__{remember the time after winter formal? when we spent four incredible hours in the hot tub...?}
